    "body": "jenshnielsen commented 15 minutes ago\n\n> Could it be related to something like this Homebrew/homebrew#30751\n> Which happens to me on OSX with readline from homebrew (independent of IPython)\n\nThat did it! Steps to fix (roughly):\n\n``` zsh\nbrew uninstall readline\nrm -rf /usr/local/Cellar/readline/\npip uninstall gnureadline\nbrew install https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Homebrew/homebrew/4237ea1c2c4c10a4c5288d11c0f0311e97f30473/Library/Formula/readline.rb\npip install https://github.com/ludwigschwardt/python-gnureadline/archive/v6.2.4.1.tar.gz\n```\n\nI will try downgrading readline on RHEL6.5 later.\n"
  },
