    "body": "I removed `gnureadline-6.3.3-py2.7-linux-x86_64.egg/` and installed [readline-6.2.4.1](https://pypi.python.org/packages/source/r/readline/readline-6.2.4.1.tar.gz#md5=578237939c81fdbc2c8334d168b17907) and reinstalled IPython and now it's good on RHEL6.5 as well. Thanks again @takluyver and everyone else.\n\nThis is pretty clearly an upstream readline problem and they are aware of it so I will close the issue.\n"
